parameters:
\SE[16]You're saying whatever you want without knowing
anything...!! About the two of us... Even though you don't
know anything...! \SE[52]I won't forgive you anymore!
\SE[46]Ouch...!! What is this, it's as hard as iron...!!

\SE[4]That's impossible, you know. \!\SE[2]Because it's all
in the memories. \.We're just replaying the records.

\SE[16]But, this is strange...! \SE[15]Suddenly throwing a
punch like that! \SE[1]I was a little surprised.

\SE[16]Because...! \SE[17]They're saying whatever they want
about Luna and Vega without even knowing them properly.
\SE[12]Causing Luna to have such a face...!!

\SE[2]That's just how it is. \SE[3]Those people are weak
after all.

\SE[2]That's right... Those people, you know. \SE[1]They
create a herd and invent a common enemy because otherwise,
they would lose. They're pitiful weak individuals.

\SE[2]They unconsciously understand that they are weak.
\!\SE[16]That's why they instinctively try to eliminate
strong individuals like this. It's selfish.

\SE[16]But even so...! \\!\SE[17]There's no justification
for hurting someone...!!

\SE[4]I don't know. \!\SE[3]After all, being weak isn't a
bad thing, right? \!\SE[4]And it's not a bad thing to be
afraid of strong people either, is it?

\SE[2]Laura has become strong... Because she started being
with strong people... \SE[15]It's becoming harder for her to
understand the feelings of weak people.

\SE[2]Well... who cares about being weak. \SE[1]If that's
all they can do, then why not let them do as they please?

\SE[16]But more importantly, you know. \SE[15]Mom is smiling
all the time. \SE[16]She was watching you just now.
\SE[16]All the time.

\SE[16]Yeah, I got it! \!\SE[0]When Laura was getting all
angry, it seemed like she was kind of happy.

\SE[16]When you started attacking, she was laughing while
holding her stomach! \SE[15]It might be the first time I've
seen Mom laugh so much...!
\SE[28]P-Please say that kind of thing beforehand...

\SE[65]But even I... I used to think of 'Lunaroa' as someone
perfect... \SE[24]I didn't really understand the truth at
all.

\SE[3]Hmm... I wonder? \SE[2]Mom seemed happiest when she
was with Laura...
\SE[65]I see... if that's the case, then...

\SE[4]That's definitely it! \.Because Mom's face right now
is completely red! \!\SE[3]She's so embarrassed, it's
unbelievable!

\SE[4]Ah! It ran away!! \.It's curled up in the corner of
the room! \!\SE[15]I've never seen anything like this
before! \.It's so cute!
\SE[71] (I kind of want to see that...)

\SE[2]Where do you want to go next? \SE[15]There are many
options, but Laura can decide.

\SE[14]My recommendation is... \!\SE[13]An unpleasant story
about being approached by nobles... \!\SE[14]A story about
demolishing a teacher's argument and causing the class to
collapse... \!\SE[16]A bloody battle between fans and anti-
fans...

\SE[43]Hmm... It's not like I want to see something
unpleasant or anything...

\SE[56]If I can choose... I want to see things that were fun
and things that were happy too. \SE[55]I'm sure there are
things that I didn't know about...

\SE[2]I see... It's not just about sharing wounds, but also
about mutual understanding.

\SE[4]Mom? \!\SE[0]Then, can you show me the one where she
was having a lot of fun?

\SE[15]Ah, I got the next one. \!\SE[15]Well then, let's go
check it out right away.
\SE[62]Yeah, if that's the case, I'll feel relieved...
\SE[5] (I wonder what Lunaroa's really fun things are...?)
